The effects of teacher human capital characteristics

2022-09-28

Outcomes of interest

  • Student academic performance (score)
  • Student academic confidence (conf)

Teacher human capital characteristics of interest

  • Educational background
    • years of education (tchedu)
    • graduate degree - masters and above (tchgrad)
    • education major (tchmajor)
  • Teaching experience
    • years of teaching (tchexp)
    • novice teacher (tchnew), dummy coded one for teachers having two year or less experience
    • a series of indicator variables (omitted first level) representing teacher experience of:
      • 0-2 years
      • 3-6 years (tchexp1)
      • 7-9 years (tchexp2)
      • 10-12 years (tchexp3)
      • 13-15 years (tchexp4)
      • 16-24 years (tchexp5)
      • more than 25 years (tchexp6)
